---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import TimeLineElement from "../components/cv/TimeLine.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Resume" sideBarActiveItemID="cv">
  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Profile</div>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-10 text-justify">
    Versatile Software Engineer with 3+ years of experience building robust, scalable applications for cloud and desktop. I
    design cloud-native microservices, responsive frontends, and AI-enabled workflows with a focus on performance,
    observability, and secure multi-tenant architectures.
  </div>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Education</div>
  </div>

  <div class="time-line-container grid gap-4 mb-10">
    <TimeLineElement
      title="B.S. Systems & Biomedical Engineering"
      subtitle="2016 – 2021 | Cairo University, Cairo, Egypt"
    />
  </div>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Experience</div>
  </div>

  <div class="time-line-container mb-10">
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Software Engineer at Voyance"
      subtitle="2023 – Present | Medical imaging platform & acquisition software"
    >
      Contributed to the end-to-end development of the VPAX cloud-native platform and VoyanceX acquisition software, working across the full stack from backend microservices to responsive ReactJS micro-frontends.
      <ul class="list-disc ml-5 mt-2">
        <li><strong>Architecture & Scale:</strong> Engineered the system to handle <strong>150x peak traffic loads</strong> and cut database costs by over <strong>30%</strong> through advanced query optimizations and caching strategies.</li>
        <li><strong>Frontend Lifecycle:</strong> Actively contributed to the full frontend lifecycle, from rapid prototyping to building production-ready features. Decreased application load times by <strong>25%</strong> by implementing a Backend-for-Frontend (BFF) pattern and optimizing the React micro-frontend.</li>
        <li><strong>Security & Design:</strong> Implemented a granular Role-Based Access Control (RBAC) system for secure multi-tenancy and authored comprehensive system design documentation to maintain system security and scalability.</li>
        <li><strong>Desktop & Hardware (VoyanceX):</strong> Developed and maintained the C# acquisition software, ensuring seamless integration with the VPAX cloud. Enhanced hardware compatibility across diverse client setups by integrating the software with new devices.</li>
        <li><strong>AI & Integrations:</strong> Integrated generative AI models into core healthcare workflows to boost practitioner efficiency and developed seamless integrations with external cloud providers like Dropbox and OneDrive.</li>
      </ul>
    </TimeLineElement>
    
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Freelance Developer"
      subtitle="2021 – 2023 | Web development"
    >
      <ul class="list-disc ml-5">
        <li>Developed and deployed custom websites for clients using technologies such as NodeJS, WordPress, and Moodle.</li>
        <li>Managed continuous client communication end-to-end to ensure delivered solutions were perfectly aligned with business needs.</li>
      </ul>
    </TimeLineElement>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Publications</div>
  </div>

  <ul class="list-disc mx-6 mb-10 grid gap-2">
    <li>
      <a href="https://doi.org/10.1109/NRSC61581.2024.10510468.2024" target="_blank">
        Cloud-Based AI-Enhanced Dual-Mode System for Coronary Artery Calcification Detection and Quantification (NRSC 2024)
      </a>
    </li>
  </ul>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Skills</div>
  </div>

  <ul class="list-disc md:columns-3 columns-2 mx-6">
    <li>JavaScript / TypeScript / Python / Java / C / C# / PHP</li>
    <li>NodeJS, NestJS, Express, Spring Boot, Flask</li>
    <li>React, Next.js, BFF patterns, performance tuning</li>
    <li>Microservices, NATS, Kubernetes, Docker, CI/CD</li>
    <li>Databases: MySQL, PostgreSQL, MongoDB, Redis, SQLite</li>
    <li>ORMs & Data: Sequelize, TypeORM, Prisma</li>
    <li>AI & Data: LangChain, RAG, PyTorch, Pandas, OpenCV</li>
    <li>Desktop & Embedded: PyQt, C#, ATmega32, hardware integration</li>
    <li>Security & Auth: JWT, RBAC, OAuth, multi-tenant isolation</li>
    <li>Cloud & DevOps: GCP, AWS, GitHub Actions, observability</li>
  </ul>
</BaseLayout>